                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000528-96-victim989 t18000528-96-viclabel555"></join> of the said Charles, did make an assault, putting her in<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="180005280093"></xptr>fear, and taking from her person, ten pounds weight of cheese, value 5s. the property of the said Charles
